&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated Sponsorships Account Manager to join our team in São Paulo. This role is ideal for a commercially driven professional with a strong hunter mentality and a passion for sports, entertainment, and cultural properties. The successful candidate will be responsible for identifying, developing, and closing new sponsorship partnerships, helping expand the league’s commercial footprint and brand ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a strategic sales role focused on business development, requiring the ability to build consultative partnerships with leading brands and agencies. This is a full time role with the expectations of 5 days in the São Paulo office in Brazil.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and prospect new sponsorship opportunities across sports, entertainment, and brand marketing sectors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain relationships with brand decision-makers, marketing leaders, and agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the full sales cycle: prospecting, pitching, negotiating, and closing sponsorship agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and position consultative partnership proposals aligned with brands’ marketing and business objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate internally with marketing, events, and partnerships teams to craft compelling sponsorship packages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain an active pipeline of qualified prospects and consistently deliver new partnership revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the league in meetings, events, and industry forums when relevant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications &amp;amp; Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5–7+ years of experience in sponsorship sales within sports, entertainment, media, or cultural properties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record in prospecting and closing partnership deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong business development mindset with a hunter profile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication, presentation, and negotiation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and manage a sales pipeline with minimal supervision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English is required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commercially driven and results-oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial and self-managed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong relationship builder with brands and agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic thinker capable of crafting consultative partnership solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are passionate about building partnerships and helping brands connect with audiences through sports and culture, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
